properties.areaDesc: San Diego County Deserts; Coachella Valley; Apple and Lucerne Valleys
properties.headline: Wind Advisory issued January 29 at 6:55AM PST until January 29 at 6:00PM PST by NWS San Diego CA
properties.description:
* WHAT...North winds 20 to 30 mph with gusts up to 55 mph
expected.

* WHERE...Apple and Lucerne Valleys, Coachella Valley and San
Diego County Deserts.

* WHEN...From 10 AM this morning to 6 PM PST this evening.

* IMPACTS...Dangerous travel for high profile vehicles on
Interstate 15 and Highways 18 and 247 in the High Desert,
Interstate 10 through the Coachella Valley, Interstate 8 and
Highway 78 in San Diego County. Gusty winds could blow around
unsecured objects. Tree limbs could be blown down and a few
power outages may result.
properties.instruction:
Use extra caution when driving, especially if operating a high
profile vehicle. Secure outdoor objects.

NWSheadline: WIND ADVISORY IN EFFECT FROM 10 AM THIS MORNING TO 6 PM PST THIS EVENING
